    ImplicitButNotExplicitPolicy<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Boolean>, ImplicitInputPolicy<java.lang.Void>, InputPolicy, Policy, StatePolicy<java.lang.Integer>

    public class FiniteSourceTerminationPolicy
extends ImplicitButNotEsplicitMaskingStateOnlyDependentPolicy<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Boolean>
    Implements the user termination policy according to which the user generation terminates as a fixed number of of users has been generated. This policy is applicable to a Source node.
    Author:
    Daniele Gianni
